    "This seems to contradict claims that few training data are provably sufficient to guarantee good generalization in QML, raised e.g. in ref.",
    "Our analytical and numerical results do not preclude the possibility of good generalization with few training data but rather indicate we cannot guarantee it with arguments based on uniform generalization bounds.",
